				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				This item is from Sol A.  (again, like my last post on an item) its hard to describe how to get to it.  But if you know the general location of the Gnome city/castle, then you are good to go.<BR>
<BR>
It is dropped by a EXG model gnome.  It doesnt always spawn (a spider of regular clockwork gnome will spawn as the placeholder).  The main way you can tell if its the EXG is that its a much bigger gnome than all the others.  It spawns right in front of the castle, but it roams.<BR>
<BR>
Its a level 30 mob, BUT its 100% magic resistant. So bring some tanks.<BR>
<BR>
The shield is its common drop (you will see it holding it), and the Charred Breatplate is its rare drop (very rare).
				</font>
			</td>

